) CHARACTER SET=utf8mb4;

    SELECT `a`.`id`, `a`.`code`, `a`.`name`, `a`.`note`
    FROM `airline` AS `a`
    WHERE `a`.`id` = @__id_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS `t`
LEFT JOIN `aircarf` AS `a0` ON `t`.`id` = `a0`.`airline_id`
ORDER BY `t`.`id`
